data.description: Nice updates in this cute 3 bedroom home. There is wood flooring throughout much of the home that's recently been refinished. Two of the bedrooms are carpeted, but there is likely wood flooring underneath. The roof was replaced in 2016 and the furnace was replaced in 2017 and there are newer windows. There's plenty of space to park 2 or more cars, or an RV in the wide driveway or even build a garage. There's lots of light in this cozy little charmer. Fully fenced front yard and the back yard is level and grassed, with room to entertain. There are some nice fruit trees blossoming right now in the back. This home is close to military bases, shopping, and schools.
